Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.27,0:00:04.02,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Even fate can be used\Nas a hint for reasoning...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:06.11,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seeing through\Nthe most mysterious cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:07.82,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today, the Detective Boys\Ntake the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:10.11,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The key that unlocks the mystery\Nis a child's drawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.11,0:00:11.65,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth\Nfor what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:13.57,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.57,0:00:15.99,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name?\NDetective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once again, it's\Nterrible, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Speak for\Nyourself, Mitsuhiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can say what you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man's worth is not\Nin the quality of his art!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:36.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But people who are good at drawing are cool\Nand I've got lots of respect for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:42.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe tomorrow,\NI'll start going to art classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:43.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, me too, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:46.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:55.07,Signs,,0,0,0,,Jukichi Sakai (55)\NSecretary to the President of\NTsubakuro Financial Group
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he's doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somehow, it smells\Nlike a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:05.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of money, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:25.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could that...be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:33.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you have\Nall that money?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:34.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No! I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:41.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Please, let me go!\NYoung master is... Young master is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...going to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:13.69,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Kenzo Tsubakuro"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:26.08,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After all, my intuition\Nwas right on the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.08,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:31.00,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A kidnapping case\Nhad occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:36.13,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The one who was kidnapped\Nwas Akio Tsubakuro{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-kun{\r\be10},
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:37.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kenzo Tsubakuro (70)\NPresident\NTsubakuro Financial Group
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:40.71,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the 5-year-old grandson of Kenzo Tsubakuro{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10},\Nthe president of the Tsubakuro Financial Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:44.63,Signs,,0,0,0,,Akio Tsubakuro (5)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:43.26,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He loves drawing pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:51.10,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And all those bills were the ransom to get Akio{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-kun{\r\be10} back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:55.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, Tsubakuro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, would you care\Nto explain to us in detail what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsubakuro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're pictures Akio drew\Nthat the kidnapper sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:11.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did you receive them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About noon yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were tossed into the mail\Nalong with the threatening letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:19.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that is the letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:30.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"¥1,000,000,000 for the child.\N—The Clown."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! I wonder how many boxed\Neel lunches I could eat for that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the money from before was nowhere near a billion yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That money was intended to check whether there\Nwas any intention of actually paying the ransom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure at the time the kidnapper was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you lot!\NWe're grateful for your tip,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but from here on in,\Nthis is police business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:08.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, hurry up\Nand go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Inspector, you lot\Nshould go home with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But, Tsubakuro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akio is my precious and only grandson, who my late son and his wife left me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:25.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when they passed on in a car crash last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If something were to happen to him,\NI would disgrace his parents in heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know how you feel,\Nbut, Tsubakuro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The moment we hand over the ransom money\Nto make contact with the culprit kidnapper
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:41.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is our perfect shot\Nat arresting him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A billion yen is quite a load,\Nso the kidnapper—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:50.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter to me\Nwhether or not you catch the kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will not risk Akio's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, I am not handing\Nover the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what do you\Nmean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was in the mailbox\Nthis morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Location for bank transfer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:15.53,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"locAtIoN foR bAnk TraNsfEr:\NfonTaUbeRt bAnk, SwiTzeRland\Naccount number: 259H604329\Nim COunTinG on You!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fontaubert Bank, Switzerland...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-A bank in Switzerland?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:21.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, we should hurry up\Nand place a chargeback,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or at least get the bank to tell us\Nwho the account holder is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Switzerland is a bank nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Swiss banks were so accomodating,\Ntheir existence would be pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:42.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it's just as the boy says.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever the case,\Nthere are no exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if doing so\Nbrings Akio back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am asking you...\NLeave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A perfect crime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Mr. Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that you gave up\Non the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't butt our way into\Npaying the ransom money
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,any further than what\NTsubakuro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} says.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:27.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the police can't just stand by idly\Nand let this dastardly crime go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So once the ransom money is handed over,\Nand Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} comes back safely,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you're gonna start seriously\Ninvestigating this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:43.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But even if the ransom {\i1}is{\i0} paid,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:47.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}there's still no guarantee Akio{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10} will come back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:54.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} sure loves to draw, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:08:59.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:08.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister, can I take another look\Nat Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As I thought,\Nit's here too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a quirk of Akio's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quirk?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he draws something, he puts down\Nwhatever catches his eye as a signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever catches his eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:40.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I've seen\Nsomething just like that somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:43.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Really? W-Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:48.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where was it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was at Beika South Kindergarten\Nwhere Akio goes to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they showed me\None of his drawings...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beika South Kindergarten, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:02.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me borrow this, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll bring it right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:11.59,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Beika South Elementary"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to take a look at\NAkio Tsubakuro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:24.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s drawings?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:27.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The drawing Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s\Ngrandfather saw
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:30.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is probably this one\Nhanging here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:34.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:40.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, teacher.\NWhere did Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} draw this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:48.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:51.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That signature is the same\Nas what Akio{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10} drew here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:56.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Furthermore, what was sent was what\Nhe drew where he was being held hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:00.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}if I can figure out where that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:05.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can make a good guess\Nas to where Akio{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10} is being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:08.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But the problem is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:09.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you up to now, Conan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't go on ahead of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:18.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're planning to rescue Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nall by yourself, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:23.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're gonna help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're dealing\Nwith a kidnapper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever danger\Nmight be waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:34.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this drawing!\NAkio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} looks like he's having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's smiling as he's watching\NTV with the kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's Kamen Yaiba, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:46.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As far as I can see from this,\Nhe doesn't seem to be in any sort of danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we're gonna save him,\Nit's now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what you were thinking,\Nwasn't it, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:58.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, aren't we the ones\Nwho found this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But only until we find\Nwhere he's being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, we leave it\Nto the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His signature?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what's this that he drew?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it an alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:21.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a chimney,\Nisn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:22.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like on a building.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah. Definitely an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would he be able\Nto see an alien from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you can't see any\Nchimneys from here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:34.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you say that,\Nyou're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no time for arguing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chimney or building,\Nit doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's split up and look for the thing\Nthat looks like this signature!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:42.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! That's it, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like a water tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It kinda looks like it\Nand it kinda doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:20.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:25.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:30.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look. What do you see\Nin front of that water tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a clock, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a park?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There isn't anything like\Na park in his signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:45.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something in the middle of the signature\Nthat looks like an eyeball.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:58.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you put the clock on top of the water tower,\Nwhat do you think it'd look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. The thing in the signature that\Nlooked like an eye was that clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:09.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s in\Nthe water tower, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:15.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant. Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s is where it\Nlooks like the clock's in front of the water tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the\Nwater tower, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can see\Nwhere Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:46.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you see over there is\Nthe park with the clock from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The eyeball in Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s signature lines up in\Nthe middle of the water tower exactly as he drew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:57.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it might be a little distorted,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:15:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} should be being held\Nsomewhere in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:06.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ugh. There's sure a lot\Nof houses around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:10.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, it doesn't look like\Nwe can really tell from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we split up and search,\Nwe should find him in no time flat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you see any suspicious\Npeople or houses,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,contact me right away\Non your badges.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't even try to\Ngive chase alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and don't think about\Ngoing to save Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:01.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were a bunch of\Nsuspicious places, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of them looked like\Nthey could be the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:09.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's still too many places\Nto narrow it down...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\Nwhere's Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:16.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were supposed to meet up\Nat the park at 5:00, weren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Ayumi here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:26.50,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-chan{\r\be10}?!\NWhere are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:28.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'d be hungry, so\NI went shopping at a convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.76,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Geez, what are we gonna\Ndo with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:39.39,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's way past when we were\Nsupposed to meet up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:40.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:43.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll head back right away,\Njust wait a—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A clown mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:53.78,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh? What was that?\NI don't copy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:59.03,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-chan{\r\be10},\Nis something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter,\NAyumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:05.79,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I found a suspicious person!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A suspicious person?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:08.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kidnapper?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:10.71,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm not sure yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.55,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but the clown that Akio drew
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:16.05,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}wore a triangular hat with\Na star on it, had green hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:18.43,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and held a remote\Nin his left hand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep, it's just like Ayumi said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:27.90,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That means that the kidnapper is left-handed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, don't do anything foolish!\NListen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:32.57,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've found him, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}... He's got to be\Nthe one who kidnapped Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:47.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna follow him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.67,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No! Stop, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-chan{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:53.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer us, Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.38,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:58.34,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But I don't want the kidnapper finding me out,\Nso wait for me to contact you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:17:58.84,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:01.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She cut us off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:07.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it! That Ayumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:22.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long are we going to wait here\Nfor Ayumi to get in touch with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be on us if\Nsomething happens to Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:36.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:40.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you use those glasses of yours\Nto find out where Ayumi is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:41.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Genta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:45.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now the Doc's got them\Nso he can fix them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, nothing's gonna happen\Njust staying here like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's search one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:54.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Search where?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:18:59.36,Dialogue,,270,0,0,,It's Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:18:59.36,Dialogue,,0,270,0,,It's Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:01.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan here!\NAre you there, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:07.04,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Tohto Coating Industrial Co., Ltd."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm back, little boy!\NAre you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:40.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bought you\Nsome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} san{\r}dwiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:41.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And some crayons\Nand drawing paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:43.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mr. Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you were out shopping, Mr. Clown,\NI did a lot of drawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you? Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:07.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! It's all right,\Nwe're here to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?\NHow did you get in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:21.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is as far as you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Kidnapper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:31.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're up against us,\Nthe Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give yourself up quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:38.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get over here, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko, there he goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:54.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:06.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:13.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Big Sis.\NI'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! What a relief!\NReally, what a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did it, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like our strategy\Nwas a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:28.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another huge victory\Nfor the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:31.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:03.40,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Afterwards, Inspector Megure and the\Nother police took our information,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:05.73,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}rushed to the scene,\Nand arrested the kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:08.44,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But as for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:10.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:15.37,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As we feared, we ended up getting\Na piece of Inspector Megure's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.45,0:23:19.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:23.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And thank you, Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.79,0:23:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's hang out again\Nsometime, Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:33.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said "Thank you"...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:36.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure feels nice when\Npeople are grateful to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:38.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.93,0:23:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} draws really well!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:44.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us see?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:51.74,Dialogue Top,,270,0,0,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:51.74,Dialogue Top,,0,270,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.74,0:23:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What's that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.95,0:23:54.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Running ahead\Nof us again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.91,0:23:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.20,0:24:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez!\NWhy does this always happen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.00,0:24:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.29,0:24:08.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A robber!\NSomeone catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.21,0:24:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He went into the alley!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.72,0:24:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the police!\NFurther escape is futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.10,0:24:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three people?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.98,0:24:33.03,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.03,0:24:37.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Next Conan's Hint: Sunglasses
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.99,0:24:38.74,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.74,0:24:41.12,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What's gonna happen to Detective\NTakagi and Detective Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.12,0:24:43.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It ain't gonna go good,\Nthat's for sure.
